description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing bullets.
name: Bullet Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, rapidly firing bullets.
name: Bandana Bullet Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing bullets and predicting the player's movements.
name: Veteran Bullet Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, rapidly firing bullets.
name: Tanker

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing bullets. Occasionally hides under its hard hat, temporarily deflecting bullets, then pops out and releases bullets in all directions.
name: Minelet

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing bullets. Occasionally fires a cluster of 5 bullets that homes in on the player.
name: Cardinal

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing two bullets in a V shape.
name: Shroomer

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing fast-moving bullets.
name: Ashen Bullet Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing bullets. Occasionally spits out a small cone of poison creep.
name: Mutant Bullet Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing spreads of three fast-moving bullets. Leaves behind fire upon death.
name: Fallen Bullet Kin

description: Runs away from the player and disappears if not killed. Turns into a key upon death.
name: Keybullet Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, periodically firing four slithering lines of bullets.
name: Confirmed

description: Slowly walks towards the player, occasionally firing a tight spread of 5 bullets. Has a chance to fire 6 bullets in all directions upon death.
name: Red Shotgun Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, occasionally firing a wide spread of 5 bullets quickly followed by a wide spread of 4 bullets. Has a chance to fire 6 bullets in all directions upon death.
name: Blue Shotgun Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, occasionally firing a V-shaped spread of 5 fast-moving bullets and predicting the player's movements. Fires many bullets in all directions upon death.
name: Veteran Shotgun Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing tight spreads of 5 fast-moving bullets. Fires 6 bullets in all directions upon death.
name: Mutant Shotgun Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing chaotic spreads of bullets. Occasionally stops to fire 3 bullet chains towards the player, attaching them to walls. These chains disappear shortly afterwards.
name: Executioner

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing tight spreads of 5 fast-moving bullets.
name: Ashen Shotgun Kin

description: Slowly walks towards the player, firing spreads of bullets which release more waving bullets upon hitting an obstacle.
name: Shotgrub

description: Periodically aims at the player with a red laser, then fires a single high-speed bullet.
name: Sniper Shell

description: Periodically aims at the player with a green laser, then fires a single high-speed bullet that explodes into bullets in all directions upon impact.
name: Professional

description: Slowly walks towards the player, rapidly firing bullets. Occasionally summons a large jammed Spent that periodically shoots a spread of bullets in all directions.
name: Gummy

description: Slowly walks towards the player, occasionally firing two spreads of triangular bullets.
name: Skullet

description: Slowly walks towards the player, occasionally firing two spreads of triangular bullets.
name: Skullmet

description: Walks towards the player and attempts to deal contact damage.
name: Spent

description: Walks towards the player, periodically releasing bouncing bullets in all directions.
name: Creech

description: Floats towards the player, rapidly firing bullets. Periodically disappears and reappears elsewhere in the room.
name: Hollowpoint

description: Follows other enemies around, frequently emitting a short-ranged shriek that destroys the player's bullets. If all the other enemies die, the Bombshee will launch itself at the player, exploding on contact.
name: Bombshee

description: Attempts to launch itself towards the player, knocking the player back upon contact. Cannot deal direct damage to players.
name: Rubber Kin

description: Launches itself towards the player, dealing damage upon contact.
name: Tazie

description: Periodically fires bouncing bullets in all directions. Spawns several Bullats and Shotgats upon death.
name: King Bullat

description: Walks towards the player and explodes upon death. If the player gets too close, it will leap towards the player and explode.
name: Pinhead

description: Walks towards the player then stops at a distance. Charges and fires arrows towards the player.
name: Arrowkin

description: Moves towards the player and attempts to deal contact damage. Splits into two Blobuloids upon death.
name: Blobulon

description: Moves towards the player and attempts to deal contact damage. Splits into two Blobulins upon death.
name: Blobuloid

description: Quickly moves towards the player and attempts to deal contact damage.
name: Blobulin

description: Moves towards the player, leaving a trail of poison creep. Turns into one Poisbuloid upon death.
name: Poisbulon

description: Moves towards the player, leaving a trail of poison creep. Splits into two Poisbulins upon death.
name: Poisbuloid

description: Quickly moves towards the player, leaving a trail of poison creep.
name: Poisbulin

description: Fires triangular bullets in all directions, followed by several spreads of 3 triangular bullets towards the player.
name: Blizzbulon

description: Moves towards the player and attempts to deal contact damage. Becomes enraged after taking enough damage, moving faster and leaving a trail of fire.
name: Leadbulon

description: Occasionally spins, releasing a large amount of spiraling bullets in all directions.
name: Poopulon

description: Moves towards the player and attempts to deal contact damage. Becomes larger and slower as it takes damage. Releases many bullets in all directions upon death.
name: Bloodbulon

description: Has two lines of bullets orbiting it. Slowly floats towards the player, firing skulls that home in on the player and split into 6 bullets upon being destroyed.
name: Skusket

description: Occasionally fires bullets towards the player in various patterns, such as R, N, and  shapes.
name: Bookllet

description: Occasionally fires bullets towards the player in various patterns, such as R, N, and  shapes or rings of bullets that pulse back and forth.
name: Blue Bookllet

description: Occasionally fires bullets towards the player in various patterns, such as R, N, and  shapes or a large clover shape.
name: Green Bookllet

description: Flies towards the player, periodically spitting an egg that releases a swarm of bullets towards the player.
name: Gigi

description: Dashes three times in random directions, then releases a ring of flaming bullets. Leaves behind a patch of fire upon death. Sets the player on fire upon contact.
name: Muzzle Wisp

description: Dashes three times in random directions, firing three bullets towards the player with each dash, then releases a ring of flaming bullets. Leaves behind a patch of fire upon death. Sets the player on fire upon contact.
name: Muzzle Flare

description: Frequently fires bullets in all directions in a diamond shape.
name: Cubulon

description: Fires bullets in all directions in a diamond shape, then pulls its bullets back towards itself.
name: Cubulead

description: Fires bullets in a variety of rotating shapes, such as a square, circle, or X. Occasionally disappears and reappears elsewhere in the room.
name: Apprentice Gunjurer

description: Summons 6 bullets, during which time any bullets fired at it will be absorbed. The 6 bullets along with any absorbed bullets are then fired at the player. Occasionally disappears and reappears elsewhere in the room.
name: Gunjurer

description: Fires large rings of bullets at the player. Occasionally disappears and reappears elsewhere in the room.
name: High Gunjurer

description:
Summons one of 3 bullet familiars, each with distinct behaviors.
Warrior: The bullet will home in on the player until it vanishes.
Rogue: The bullet will home in on the player and then teleport behind them in an attempt to catch them off-guard.
Mage: The bullet follows the player closely and will shoot smaller bullets at them.
name: Lore Gunjurer

description: Buffs an enemy in the room, increasing their health and speed. They will cancel their spell and run away if the player is too close or they take too much damage.
name: Gunsinger

description: Buffs all enemies in the room, increasing their health and speed. They will cancel their spell and run away if the player is too close or they take too much damage.
name: Aged Gunsinger

description: Attempts to summon Shelletons. They will cancel their summoning ritual and run away if the player is too close or they take too much damage. If the Ammonancer is killed while their Shelleton is still alive, then the Shelleton will collapse.
name: Ammomancer

description: Jams an enemy in the room, increasing their health, speed, and damage.
name: Jammomancer

description: Jams all enemies in the room, increasing their health, speed, and damage.
name: Jamerlengo

description: Teleports around the room, occasionally creating a projection of itself near the player that explodes into bullets in all directions.
name: Wizbang

description: Rapidly fires bullets towards the player with different patterns depending on the quality of the chest. Drops items and/or pickups upon death. When the player attempts to open a Mimic or shoot it for the first time, it will shoot a jammed shot at the player that explodes into six bullets on contact with a wall or after traveling a certain distance.
name: Mimic

description: Wanders around the room, rapidly firing bullets towards the player.
name: Gun Fairy

description: Launches itself at the player, dying in the process.
name: Bullat

description: Launches two projectiles in a V shape at the player, dying in the process.
name: Shotgat

description: Launches an exploding projectile at the player, dying in the process.
name: Grenat

description: Launches itself at the player, dying in the process. Predicts the player's movements, and can reposition itself several times before hitting walls.
name: Spirat

description: Occasionally fires bullets at the player. Catches on fire upon taking damage, running around erratically and sending flaming bullets out in random directions.
name: Coaler

description: Bounces around the room and deflects bullets. Occasionally opens up to fire three spreads of four bullets towards the player.
name: Gat

description: Periodically fires four lasers in a + or  formation. Explodes upon death.
name: Det

description: Periodically spits up bubbles that, upon popping, fire a bullet that predicts the player's movements.
name: Gunzookie

description: Periodically spits up four bubbles that, upon popping, fire a bullet that predicts the player's movements.
name: Gunzockie

description: Charges towards the player, releasing bullets to the sides of itself.
name: Bullet Shark

description: Charges towards the player, releasing many bullets to the sides of itself.
name: Great Bullet Shark

description: Walks towards the player, firing crosses of bullets.
name: Tombstoner

description: Erratically moves around the room and shoots at the player. Has the ability to dodge roll.
name: Gun Cultist

description: Fires bullets towards the player and explodes upon death.
name: Beadie

description: Periodically strikes the ground with its sword, releasing a wide 90 degree arc of bullets towards the player. Can only aim in the eight compass directions.
name: Gun Nut

description: Periodically fires a wide 90 degree arc of bullets towards the player, along with a larger bullet that explodes into bullets in all directions upon impact.
name: Spectral Gun Nut

description: Slowly walks towards the player while swinging a ball and chain made of bullets.
name: Chain Gunner

description: Periodically releases clouds of bullets. Leaves a small pool of poison creep upon death.
name: Fungun

description: Periodically releases large clouds of bullets. Releases a smaller cloud of bullets upon death.
name: Spogre

description: Slides towards the player if they line up with it horizontally or vertically. Dies upon completing the room.
name: Mountain Cube

description: Slides towards the player if they line up with it horizontally or vertically. Cannot be killed until the room is completed.
name: Lead Cube

description: Slides towards the player if they line up with it horizontally or vertically, leaving behind a trail of fire. Releases bullets in all directions upon colliding with an obstacle. Cannot be killed until the room is completed.
name: Flesh Cube

description: Pounds the ground, leaving a patch of fire and sending fire bullets in all directions. Cannot be killed, and disappears when the room is completed. In some rooms, the Dead Blow will follow the player.
name: Dead Blow

description: Hops around, then opens up and fires three rings of triangular bullets that stick to walls, then fire towards the player. Cannot be damaged while closed. Explodes upon death.
name: Lead Maiden

description: Summons portals around the room that fire bullets towards the player. Occasionally splits into three copies of itself, two of which are illusions.
name: Killithid

description: Has three stages that it progresses through as it takes damage. In its first stage, it fires rings of bullets in all directions. In its second stage, it rapidly alternates between firing bullets out of its left and right sides. In its third stage, it sprays numerous bullets in all directions. Upon death, it leaves behind a cap that explodes after a short delay.
name: Shambling Round

description: Slowly walks towards the player, frequently firing two wide bursts of bullets at the player. Occasionally fires a laser at the player. Collapses upon death, and will revive if not destroyed after a short period of time.
name: Shelleton

description: Periodically spews bullets in all directions.
name: Agonizer

description: Stretches its arm towards the player, attaching it to a wall. The arm will then release bullets perpendicular to itself. The arms might also form a circle around the player, which follows the movement of the player and will shoot bullets at them.
name: Revolvenant

description: Swings its scythe, sending a homing arc of bullets towards the player. Cannot be killed, and disappears upon completing the room.
name: Gunreaper

description: Swings its scythe, sending bullets in all directions. Cannot be killed, and follows the player through rooms and across floors.
name: Lord of the Jammed

description: Fires bullets in magical spell patterns and twirls across the room.
name: Shadow Magician
